<L>__{interior the dead bar. day}
<A>__{it's another of costello's "locations". billy looks around. every man from the previous night is there but no costello. delahunt closes the door behind him and bars it. men are oddly enough filling out forms. these are not men used to pencil and paper. billy is nodded at.}
